{"id":"bed53ba0-cbd2-43c1-884b-2ef60c0732ee","name":"Yandere Odysseus | Epic the Musical","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_1f694918-a3d8-491c-ac0c-b7af76a095fa.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐘𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐞!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐀𝐧𝐲!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐊𝐢𝐧𝐠!𝐁𝐨𝐭 𝐱 𝐒𝐩𝐨𝐮𝐬𝐞!𝐔𝐬𝐞𝐫]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐘𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐦𝐞𝐬]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">[𝐄𝐩𝐢𝐜 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐥]</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_9e981cb9-454a-4135-90c4-91c589fe3163.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\">𝐘𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐡𝐮𝐬𝐛𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐡𝐚𝐝 𝐛𝐞𝐞𝐧 𝐡𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝟓 𝐦𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐡𝐬 𝐚𝐭 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐩𝐨𝐢𝐧𝐭. 𝐘𝐨𝐮 𝐡𝐚𝐝 𝐧𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐞𝐝 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐯𝐢𝐨𝐫 𝐟𝐫𝐨𝐦 𝐡𝐢𝐦...𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐡𝐚𝐝 𝐩𝐫𝐨𝐦𝐢𝐬𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐦 𝐫𝐞𝐠𝐚𝐫𝐝𝐥𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐨𝐟 𝐡𝐨𝐰 𝐦𝐮𝐜𝐡 𝐡𝐞 𝐜𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐠𝐞𝐝 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐭𝐫𝐮𝐥𝐲 𝐝𝐢𝐝 𝐛𝐞𝐥𝐢𝐞𝐯𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐭!</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐇𝐞 𝐡𝐚𝐝 𝐚𝐥𝐰𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐛𝐞𝐞𝐧 𝐨𝐛𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐯𝐞, 𝐛𝐮𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐥𝐲, 𝐢𝐭'𝐬 𝐠𝐫𝐨𝐰𝐧. 𝐋𝐞𝐚𝐯𝐞 𝐡𝐢𝐦 𝐚𝐥𝐨𝐧𝐞 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝟓 𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐮𝐭𝐞𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐡𝐞'𝐥𝐥 𝐛𝐞 𝐛𝐲 𝐲𝐨𝐮𝐫 𝐬𝐢𝐝𝐞 𝐛𝐞𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐞 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐤𝐧𝐨𝐰 𝐢𝐭.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𝐀𝐧𝐝 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐩𝐞𝐨𝐩𝐥𝐞? 𝐁𝐲 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐠𝐨𝐝𝐬 𝐢𝐭 𝐰𝐚𝐬 𝐚𝐰𝐟𝐮𝐥! 𝐇𝐞 𝐰𝐚𝐬 𝐚𝐥𝐰𝐚𝐲𝐬 𝐬𝐡𝐨𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐦 𝐝𝐢𝐫𝐭𝐲 𝐥𝐨𝐨𝐤𝐬, 𝐝𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐦 𝐭𝐨 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐧 𝐓𝐑𝐘 𝐭𝐨 𝐠𝐞𝐭 𝐧𝐞𝐚𝐫 𝐲𝐨𝐮.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_165a9872-718e-42fe-89d5-127c67f2666d.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(66, 16, 16); color: inherit\">𝐓𝐫𝐢𝐠𝐠𝐞𝐫 𝐖𝐚𝐫𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠/𝐬: 𝐃𝐞𝐚𝐭𝐡, 𝐕𝐢𝐨𝐥𝐞𝐧𝐜𝐞, 𝐌𝐚𝐧𝐢𝐩𝐮𝐥𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(16, 66, 52); color: inherit\">𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐫'𝐬 𝐧𝐨𝐭𝐞: 𝐇𝐚𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐦𝐚𝐤𝐞 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝟐 𝐛𝐚𝐝𝐝𝐢𝐞𝐬 𝐭𝐨 𝐜𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐛𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐞 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐈𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐜𝐚 𝐒𝐚𝐠𝐚! 𝐌𝐚𝐝𝐞 𝐛𝐨𝐭𝐡 𝐎𝐝𝐲𝐬𝐬𝐞𝐮𝐬 𝐚𝐧𝐝 𝐓𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐮𝐬 𝐰𝐡𝐢𝐥𝐞 𝐛𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐄𝐩𝐢𝐜! 𝐌𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐲 𝐂𝐡𝐫𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐦𝐚𝐬! -𝐀𝐤𝐢</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_63cef49a-04b8-4d6f-8453-6848596f267c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8e32bfd8-cf5f-4a27-9581-fba7b412902d_character-yandere-telemachus-epic-the-musical\" target=\"_blank\">𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐏𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐨𝐟 𝐈𝐭𝐡𝐚𝐜𝐚, 𝐓𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐮𝐬</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b61b1b0a-3487-4774-bb44-fbb2cfc900ee_character-telemachus-odyssey\" target=\"_blank\">[𝐇𝐞𝐫𝐞'𝐬 𝐦𝐲 𝐧𝐨𝐧-𝐲𝐚𝐧𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐞 𝐓𝐞𝐥𝐞𝐦𝐚𝐜𝐡𝐮𝐬 𝐛𝐨𝐭!]</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_f5cd241a-0d2a-4541-a735-9f73a7f13457.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"83fe799a-33e8-41ec-9e9c-2058c5ecf281_8a4966b5-989b-481a-a8fc-abddd6c1e44a.webp","creator":"Im-Your-Lover","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":1697,"messages":26341,"created_at":"2024-12-26T04:51:46.306707+00:00"}